Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這場地震　可能和悠羅有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅…　悠羅妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡！　這些事情　一定和遺產有關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…對了！　一定是他！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是那小子幹的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅　悠羅到底在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅　悠羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　你果然　還是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在哪裡？　妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在我勉強封印了　卡斯多爾的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以請你珍惜時間　把卡斯多爾打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「卡斯多爾」是指這個巨人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後呢？　悠羅妳會怎辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是你與史雷因　及其他許多人在尋找的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舊世界的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是遺產嗎？　是這傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯！　和悠羅同類！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅…　和這巨人同類？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯！　詳情我也不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽說到帝國的圖書館的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就可以知道很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裘朗　原來你是帝都的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所謂的聖靈力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可分為悠羅　及亞米雷特這兩大類別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道這種巨人還有幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有他一個？\N還是尚有很多很多個沉眠於大陸各處？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之　是這個傢伙毀滅舊世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在　仍可能危害大陸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不！　是全世界的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等　所以悠羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就悠羅和亞米雷特來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算摧毀不了對方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少也可以把對方封印起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,換句話說…\N史雷因那傢伙　喚醒了不該喚醒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…　這麼說就不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你　先把悠羅喚醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊？　怎麼扯到我頭上來？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他快醒過來了　得趕快想辦法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個我也…　不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看是需要那個亞米雷特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不動手的話　就讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把亞米雷特交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在我暫時封印了卡斯多爾的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡！　沒有別的辦法了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要照著辦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德　撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅！　悠羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳在哪裡？　悠羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺好像有人在喊我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當我想是誰在喊我時　就出現了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了　無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅　怎麼了？（悠羅　妳怎麼了？）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,精靈的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,精靈的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,精靈的力量無法仰止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能跟你在一起離開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅　妳在胡說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卡斯多爾的身體消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,封印在他體內的精靈力量　被釋放出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去寄宿的地方無處可去　失控的四處奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去控制的精靈　只是單純的力量的聚合體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再過不久　這裡將…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不！　不單這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切張會消去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼…　趕快尋找出逃離這裡的方法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行的！　就算逃離洞窟　不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿比爾鎮也逃不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全世界都會面臨毀滅　是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…　怎會有這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…　那該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我的使命　只有我可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼？　為什麼是妳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　能封印它們的只有我和卡斯多爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等啊，悠羅！　住手啊，悠羅！\N那麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不阻止失控的精靈　一切都將會失去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包括我重視的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前我太慌張了　對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然被人說自己不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,任何人聽到都會愣然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！　不過我已經沒問題了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經…　能冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅　難道妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳的記憶恢復了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯！　那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過　我真是　很感激你　海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感激？　感激我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！　所以要向你道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別這樣！　別客氣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛開始讓我從沉睡中甦醒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及拯救我脫離困境的都是海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當我以為不行時　和陷入危機時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生你就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想到　因為海德先生找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才能站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心裡　就覺得好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的命運　是海德先生給予的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且櫻花小姐、靜木醫生、瑪麗亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和許多人的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家對我都那麼的親切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚至連我的來歷都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些事　悠羅妳也不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家是喜歡悠羅　才自然地幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然　我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最喜歡大家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳有這份心意　就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯！　謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你　海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直　依賴著海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生不在身邊的話　我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想永遠這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　我的心跳得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是　卻又感到很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然不知道為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卻是第一次有這種舒服的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊！　那麼…　就讓妳更舒服吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅的身體　真是美極了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　那裡好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊！　好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了　把我放進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生的這根…　又硬又熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在悠羅的體內時會更熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣　慢慢坐下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛不痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣我們合為一體了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在　與海德先生變成一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生的那個　在我體內一下一下的跳動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為悠羅的身體太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最喜歡海德先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也最喜歡悠羅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…　怎麼說…　有點害羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…　我覺得…　無法…　忍受了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係的　妳儘量的動吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉！　弄痛妳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是！　只是感到　怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的身體　會麻痺的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生一動　全身就麻痺起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,覺得舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行　快瘋掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是　快射了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德先生　好熱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的那裡　變得好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得　幸福極了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行　我不許妳那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悠羅　我不能讓妳犧牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是為了和你見面　而待在這個洞窟的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見了　海德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.43,0:26:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以後見…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.31,0:26:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次見…　Bye Bye…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.03,0:26:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.40,0:26:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi……
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.50,0:27:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊！　櫻花　妳誤會了　這件事說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.20,0:27:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實在是件很複雜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.00,0:27:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我發誓什麼也沒做過　為何妳的臉色那麼難看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.83,0:27:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是說　我真的是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.42,0:27:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼這種事要發生在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.93,0:27:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德　這種時候你總是碰巧在附近轉圈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.01,0:27:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不！　不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.93,0:27:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德　你想去哪裡　給我回來　混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.31,0:27:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！　瑪娜緹，妳好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.23,0:27:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回頭見！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.73,0:27:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢點　海德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.61,0:27:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等　混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.03,0:27:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.21,0:27:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.34,0:27:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！　那邊兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.67,0:28:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們看來相處得相當好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.28,0:28:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回頭見啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.85,0:28:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站住　你這混蛋　海德！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.93,0:28:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然遇到很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.82,0:28:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想我會繼續在　阿比爾逗留一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.02,0:28:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我去下一個遺跡尋找寶物之前
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.44,0:28:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然，會和櫻花一起去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.03,0:28:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海德！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.70,0:28:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,～劇終～